name: Breast Press LoRA
description:
LoRA for generating images with the "Breast Press" pose

LoRA request queue: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1DXjs-96citoEa4NPWWxm4o92kQyrJpgdXQGWQg65oiM/edit?usp=sharing

This model was trained using 110 images on the NAI model. Most of them were NSFW, so that's what you will mainly get unless you specify it otherwise. I only tried it with 2 girls so far, might also work for futa or with a guy.

Works best by itself but with some inpainting you can get it to work with other character LoRA's.

I got the best results with a weight between 0.6 and 0.75.

Trigger word is breast press but I recommend adding 2girls to make it consistent when using other LoRA's. Add kissing and closed eyes if you want to achieve that pose. Add nipples to the negative prompt if you want the chest area to look cleaner.

Example images were generated using AOM2 hard on Euler A with 20 steps.

EDIT:

Male on female does not work, for futa on female just generate the image normally, then inpaint the futa dick since it also doesnt generate it well on its own. Also I did not clarify this before but it only got trained for the pose in the examples.
